  <h2>Where to start</h2>
  <p style="color:var(--ink-soft);max-width:70ch"><strong>This week:</strong> load the SMB cadence into HubSpot (it's written) + ship the "DIY vs. Clerri" piece. <strong>Next:</strong> the write-off calculator (the owner-dentist magnet that feeds the cadence) + the CFO/RCM ABM touch for your top target accounts. <strong>Then:</strong> the patient-facing "what membership covers" set (practice-deployable, feeds <a href="/clerri/patient-acquisition">patient acquisition</a>). Everything cross-links to the <a href="/clerri/competitors">battlecard</a> and <a href="/clerri/content-bank">content bank</a>.</p>

